item.title: There is No “I” in Perfect
item.description: In a world where the unspoken standard is perfection, how do we trust that we are worthy even though we are inherently imperfect? In this episode, we uncover the next Yoni Code with this powerfully relevant conversation. Don’t miss: ● How we can work with and embrace our imperfection ● How the pursuit of perfection paralyzes us and keeps us from growth and expansion ● The part of ourselves that gets lost in the quest for perfection ● How to find the joy in being Imperfect Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/the-yoni-codes/
